question: Will Jake Paul or Tyron Woodley win their boxing match?
description: This is a market on whether Jake Paul or Tyron Woodley will win their bout, set to take place on August 29, 2021. If Jake Paul is declared the winner of this bout, either by knockout or judgement, this market will resolve to “Paul.” If Tyron Woodley is declared the winner, either by knockout or judgement, this market will resolve to “Woodley.” If this fight is declared a draw, or the match is not scored for any reason, each side will resolve to $0.50. If this match is for any reason postponed or canceled, and not rescheduled/completed by September 30, 2021, each side will resolve to $0.50. In the event of ambiguity in terms of the market outcome, the market will be resolved at the sole discretion of the Markets Integrity Committee (MIC).
